OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773806609
OL,3,CRayner warns Labour 'running out of
OL,4,Ctime' and 'survival of party at stake'
OL,6,FAngela Rayner has warned Labour is
OL,7,F"running out of time" to deliver
OL,8,Fchange and cannot "go through the
OL,9,Fmotions in the face of decline" in an
OL,10,Fapparent challenge to Sir Keir
OL,11,FStarmer's leadership.
OL,13,FIn a speech at an event by campaign
OL,14,Fgroup Mainstream, the former deputy
OL,15,Fprime minister said the party had come
OL,16,Fto be seen to represent "the
OL,17,FEstablishment, not working people" and
OL,18,Fcalled for a change of course.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@UO]pD@SOUqD@_O]xD@YOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
