OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773806609
OL,3,CRayner warns Labour 'running out of
OL,4,Ctime' and 'survival of party at stake'
OL,6,FMs Rayner cited immigration reform as
OL,7,Fa key concern, suggesting that changes
OL,8,Fto indefinite leave to remain for
OL,9,Fpeople already living in Britain would
OL,10,Fbe a "breach of trust".
OL,12,FIn an apparent attack on Shabana
OL,13,FMahmood's plans to overhaul the
OL,14,Fsystem, she said: "Many people came
OL,15,Fhere to Britain ` on the understanding
OL,16,Fthat if they worked in the sectors
OL,17,Fwhere we needed them, obeyed the law
OL,18,Fand paid their taxes, they could stay.
OL,26,@rD@FOUrD@VO]vD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773806609
OL,3,CRayner warns Labour 'running out of
OL,4,Ctime' and 'survival of party at stake'
OL,6,F"If we suddenly change that, it pulls
OL,7,Fthe rug from under those who have
OL,8,Fplanned their lives and commitments
OL,9,Fand are contributing to our economy
OL,10,Fand to our society.
OL,12,F"That would be not just bad policy but
OL,13,Fa breach of trust. The people already
OL,14,Fin the system ` who made a huge
OL,15,Finvestment ` now fear for their
OL,16,Ffuture, they do not have stability and
OL,17,Fdo not know what will happen.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773806609
OL,3,CRayner warns Labour 'running out of
OL,4,Ctime' and 'survival of party at stake'
OL,6,F"We cannot talk about earning a
OL,7,Fsettlement if we keep moving the
OL,8,Fgoalposts, because moving the
OL,9,Fgoalposts undermines our sense of fair
OL,10,Fplay. It's un-British."
OL,12,FThe Home Secretary has announced plans
OL,13,Fto double the time it takes for
OL,14,Fmigrants to qualify for permanent
OL,15,Fresidence from five to 10 years,
OL,16,Farguing that long-term settlement is a
OL,17,F"privilege" that must be earned.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@WO]yD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
