CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773806609
OL,3,CRayner warns Labour 'running out of
OL,4,Ctime' and 'survival of party at stake'
OL,6,FOther requirements, such as speaking
OL,7,FEnglish to a higher standard, will
OL,8,Falso need to be met in order to stay
OL,9,Fin Britain, the Government has said.
OL,11,FMs Rayner said: "As a party, and as a
OL,12,Fmovement, we cannot hide, we cannot
OL,13,Fjust go through the motions in the
OL,14,Fface of decline.
OL,16,F"There's no safe ground and we're
OL,17,Frunning out of time.
OL,26,@sD@QOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773806609
OL,3,CRayner warns Labour 'running out of
OL,4,Ctime' and 'survival of party at stake'
OL,6,F"The change that people wanted so
OL,7,Fdesperately needs to be seen, it needs
OL,8,Fto be felt, and we have to show that
OL,9,Fit is a Labour government that will
OL,10,Fdeliver it."
OL,12,FMs Rayner resigned as housing
OL,13,Fsecretary and deputy prime minister
OL,14,Flast year after a row over her
OL,15,Funderpayment of stamp duty on a new
OL,16,Fproperty.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
