OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773806609
OL,3,CRayner warns Labour 'running out of
OL,4,Ctime' and 'survival of party at stake'
OL,6,FShe has since been widely seen as a
OL,7,Fpotential successor to Sir Keir amid
OL,8,Frumblings of a leadership challenge as
OL,9,Fboth Labour's poll ratings and the
OL,10,FPrime Minister's personal approval
OL,11,Fflounder.
OL,13,FMs Rayner spoke at Mainstream after
OL,14,FTony Vaughan, who has co-ordinated a
OL,15,Fletter said to have been signed by
OL,16,Fmore than 100 Labour parliamentarians
OL,17,Furging the Government to rethink its
OL,18,Fimmigration proposals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
