PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773806609
OL,3,CRayner warns Labour 'running out of
OL,4,Ctime' and 'survival of party at stake'
OL,6,FThe Home Secretary has argued that
OL,7,FLabour values have guided the changes
OL,8,Fbut that firm but fair action is
OL,9,Fneeded.
OL,11,FIn a speech earlier this month, she
OL,12,Fsaid: "Restoring order and control at
OL,13,Four border is not a betrayal of Labour
OL,14,Fvalues, it is an embodiment of them,
OL,15,Fand it is the necessary condition for
OL,16,Fa Labour Government to achieve
OL,17,Fanything it hopes to."
OL,26,@tD@GOUyD@VO]
